}


<header class="masthead">
    <div class="header-content">
        <div class="header-content-inner text-white">
            <h1>Welcome to GRSPay Server</h1>
            <hr />
            <p>GRSPay Server is a free and open source server for merchants wanting to accept Groestlcoin for their business.</p>
